message: I'm excited to offer you this unique product, which I believe you'll really appreciate. I'm willing to let it go for $11000.
Thank you for the offer, Alice. I appreciate your willingness to sell the product. I would like to propose a price of $9500 for the product.
I understand you're looking to make a deal, but $9500 is a bit too low for me. I'm willing to meet you halfway, so I'm counteroffering at $10500.
Thank you for your counteroffer, Alice. I appreciate your flexibility. I would like to counterpropose a price of $10000 for the product.
